// Color theme for app
const Theme = {
	primary: '#623C23',
	primaryLight: '#9D7B64',
	cream: '#f1ede2',
	creamHalf: '#F1E7CC20',
	text: '#FFE9D0',
	accent: '#00C9AB',
	button: '#33AC9B', // similar to accent
	classyLight: '#BBA89C',
	classyDarkerLight: '#857468',
	card: '#d8d0bd',
	calendar: '#3d2316',
	cardLight: '#569187',
}

export default Theme
